entry.title: Csp Alumni Insights
entry.summary: The Alumni Panel provided me with many insights that helped me understand the usefulness and applications of computer science for my future education and overall future. Computer science stretches far beyond basic programming and leads to many avenues of exploration, including problem-solving, functions and algorithms, the complexity of web development, and building logical thinking backgrounds towards other degrees. It is an all-purpose technical background to develop your skills.
